To setup a Pi:

Copy the files into the following locations on the Pi:
interfaces -> /etc/network/interfaces (must use sudo)
rc.local -> /etc/rc.local (must use sudo)
wpa_supplicant.conf -> /etc/wpa_supplicant/wpa_supplicant.conf (must use sudo)
tcp_serial_redirect0.py -> ~pi/tcp_serial_redirect0.py
tcp_serial_redirect_wrapper.py -> ~pi/tcp_serial_redirect_wrapper.py

To get a static IP Address:

Send MAC address to Mike Horne so he can setup a DHCP reservation for OLIN-ROBOTICS
